  ID: MenAtArms2
  Name: Francisco
  Icon: {fileID: -2105629146, guid: d556a7f542c7d03429c5a535ce31a084, type: 3}
  Description: "Wound: Right hand mangled beyond repair by a pike thrust, bones protruding,
    skin torn.\n\nStory: Francisco, a blacksmith from Castile, thrashes with rage
    rather than pain. He forged the very weapons the knights now wield, and without
    his hand he sees himself as useless iron \u2014 broken, discarded. He screams
    that his family name will die with him if he cannot even work his forge again.\n\n\nRequired
    bandages to heal: 3"
  slotNumber: 1
  requiredResource: Bandage
  requiredAmount: 3
